            shape:
                RoundedRectangleBorder(borderRadius: BorderRadius.circular(16)),
          ),
          onPressed: _signOut,
        ),
      ),
    );
  }
}

// ─── SHARED WIDGETS ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
class _Card extends StatelessWidget {
  final Widget child;
  final EdgeInsets margin;
  const _Card({required this.child, this.margin = EdgeInsets.zero});

  @override
